original_body_lines: The Malaysian High Commission in Sri Lanka celebrated Eid festival with the patronage of Minister of Foreign Affairs Ali Sabry in Colombo on May 6, 2023. Media and Transport Minister Bandula Gunawardena, Malaysian High Commissioner to Sri Lanka Tan Yang Thai and Chinese envoy to Sri Lanka Qi Zhenhong are seen sharing lighter moments during the event. Pix by PradeepPathirana.
